insert  into `cnvd`(`ID`,`CNVD_ID`,`RELEASE_TIME`,`HAZARD_LEVEL`,`AFFECT_GOODS`,`CVE_ID`,`DESCRIPTION`,`REFER_LINK`,`SOLUTION`,`FINDER`,`PATCH`,`VERIFY`,`REPORT_TIME`,`RECORD_TIME`,`RENEW_TIME`,`BUGTRAQ_ID`,`CREATE_TIME`,`LAST_TIME`,`CNVD_NAME`,`OTHER_ID`,`CNVD_TYPE`) values (1,'CNVD-2016-03894','2016-06-12 00:00:00','高 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:N/I:N/A:C)','SIEMENS SIMATIC S7-300 CPUs with Profinet support < V3.2.12 \r\nSIEMENS SIMATIC S7-300 CPUs without Profinet support < V3.3.12','CVE-2016-3949','Siemens SIMATIC S7-300 CPU是西门子（Siemens）公司的一款用于制造行业的模块化通用控制器。 \r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-300 CPU系列设备存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者利用漏洞在一定条件下可发起拒绝服务攻击，即通过发送精心编制的数据包到102/ TCP（ISO-TSAP）端口或现场总线Profibus，导致设备进入故障模式，冷启动可恢复系统。','http://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-818183.pdf','厂商已发布了新版本修复该漏洞，请及时下载更新： \r\nhttps://support.industry.siemens.com/cs/ww/en/ps/13752',' Mate J. Csorba, DNV GL, Marine Cybernetics Service；Amund Sole, Norwegian University of Science and Technology','Siemens SIMATIC S7-300 CPU拒绝服务漏洞的补丁','','2016-06-12 00:00:00','2016-06-12 00:00:00','2016-06-12 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 18:36:55','2016-10-27 18:36:56','Siemens SIMATIC S7-300 CPU拒绝服务漏洞','',NULL),(2,'CNVD-2016-00931','2016-02-16 00:00:00','高 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:N/I:N/A:C)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500 CPU family <V1.8.3','CVE-2016-2200','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500是模块化结构的控制器系列产品。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1500 1.8.3之前的版本在处理特制的TCP数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者利用漏洞可使CPU自动重启并停留在STOP模式，需要手动进入RUN模式。','http://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-253230.pdf','厂商发布了1.8.3版本修复该漏洞，请到厂商主页下载更新： \r\nhttps://support.industry.siemens.com/cs/de/en/view/109478459 ','Siemens','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500拒绝服务漏洞（CNVD-2016-00931 ）的补丁','','2016-02-15 00:00:00','2016-02-16 00:00:00','2016-02-16 00:00:00','','2016-11-02 12:08:19','2016-11-02 12:08:19','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500拒绝服务漏洞','',NULL),(3,'CNVD-2016-01756','2016-03-22 00:00:00','中 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:P/I:P/A:N)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU < V4.0','CVE-2016-2846','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU device是德国西门子（Siemens）公司的一款满足中小型自动化系统需求的小型可编程控制器。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU 4.0以前的版本存在权限绕过漏洞，攻击者利用漏洞可特定情况下绕过用户程序保护模块。 ','http://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-833048.pdf','厂商已发布安全公告修复该漏洞，请及时下载更新： \r\nhttps://support.industry.siemens.com/cs/document/106200276/firmware-version-v4-1-released-for-s7-12',' Maik Brüggemann','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU权限绕过漏洞的补丁','','2016-03-15 00:00:00','2016-03-22 00:00:00','2016-03-22 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 19:06:20','2016-10-27 19:06:20','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU权限绕过漏洞','',NULL),(4,'CNVD-2016-00930','2016-02-16 00:00:00','低 (AV:N/AC:H/Au:N/C:N/I:P/A:N)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500 CPU family <V1.8.3 ','CVE-2016-2201','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500是模块化结构的控制器系列产品。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1500存在绕过机制漏洞。远程攻击者利用该漏洞，借助TCP 102端口上的特制的数据包可绕过重放保护机制。','http://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-253230.pdf','厂商发布了1.8.3版本修复该漏洞，请到厂商主页下载更新： \r\nhttps://support.industry.siemens.com/cs/de/en/view/109478459 ',' Siemens','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500绕过机制漏洞的补丁','','2016-02-15 00:00:00','2016-02-16 00:00:00','2016-02-16 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 19:05:40','2016-10-27 19:05:41','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500绕过机制漏洞','',NULL),(5,'CNVD-2015-07953','2015-12-25 00:00:00','低 (AV:L/AC:H/Au:N/C:P/I:P/A:P)','Siemens APOGEE Insight 3.12\r\nSiemens APOGEE Insight 3.13','','Insight是西门子楼宇自控系统APOGEE中用到的监控组态软件。 \r\n\r\nSiemens APOGEE Insight Database Conversion Tool存在DLL劫持漏洞。由于Insight的Database Conversion组件Convert.exe程序不安全装载库文件（指向atlas.dll文件），攻击者可通过构造恶意应用置放于特定路径中，可使应用恶意加载DLL并执行。','','','  中国电子科技网络信息安全有限公司、湖南省产商品质量监督检验研究院 ','Siemens APOGEE Insight Database Conversion Tool DLL劫持漏洞','','2015-11-10 00:00:00','2015-12-08 00:00:00','2016-06-30 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 19:02:12','2016-10-27 19:02:13','Siemens APOGEE Insight Database Conversion Tool DLL劫持漏洞','',NULL),(6,'CNVD-2015-07864','2015-12-01 00:00:00','高 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:P/I:C/A:C)','Siemens SIMATIC CP 343-1 Advanced devices <3.0.44\r\nSiemens CP 343-1 Lean devices \r\nSiemens CP 343-1 devices \r\nSiemens TIM 3V-IE devices \r\nSiemens TIM 3V-IE Advanced devices \r\nSiemens TIM 3V-IE DNP3 devices \r\nSiemens TIM 4R-IE devices \r\nSiemens TIM 4R-IE DNP3 devices \r\nSiemens CP 443-1 devices \r\nSiemens CP 443-1 Advanced devices ','CVE-2015-8214','Siemens SIMATIC CP 343-1/TIM 3V-IE/TIM 4R-IE/CP 443-1是通信机模块。 \r\nSiemens SIMATIC CP 343-1 Advanced 设备3.0.44之前版本, CP 343-1 Lean, CP 343-1, TIM 3V-IE, TIM 3V-IE Advanced, TIM 3V-IE DNP3, TIM 4R-IE, TIM 4R-IE DNP3, CP 443-1, CP 443-1 Advanced在访问保护层的实现上存在安全漏洞，允许未经身份验证的远程攻击者利用此漏洞通过TCP端口102上的会话获取管理员访问权限。','http://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-763427.pdf','目前厂商已经发布了升级补丁以修复这个安全问题，请到厂商的主页下载： \r\nhttp://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-763427.pdf',' Lei ChengLin ','Siemens SIMATIC通信机模块信息泄露漏洞的补丁','','2015-11-30 00:00:00','2015-12-01 00:00:00','2015-12-01 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 19:00:06','2016-10-27 19:00:06','Siemens SIMATIC通信机模块信息泄露漏洞','',NULL),(7,'CNVD-2015-05789','2015-09-06 00:00:00','中 (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:P/I:P/A:P)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU','CVE-2015-5698 ','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU device是德国西门子（Siemens）公司的一款充分满足于中小型自动化系统需求的小型可编程控制器。 \r\n\r\n使用4.1.3之前版本固件的Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU设备中的Web服务器中存在跨站请求伪造漏洞。远程攻击者可利用该漏洞执行未授权操作。','https://ics-cert.us-cert.gov/advisories/ICSA-15-239-02','目前厂商已经发布了升级补丁以修复这个安全问题，请到厂商的主页下载： https://support.industry.siemens.com/cs/ww/en/ps/13685/dl',' ICS-CERT ','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU设备跨站请求伪造漏洞的补丁','','2015-09-01 00:00:00','2015-09-06 00:00:00','2015-09-06 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 18:59:11','2016-10-27 18:59:11','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU设备跨站请求伪造漏洞','',NULL),(8,'CNVD-2015-01606','2015-03-13 00:00:00','高 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:N/I:N/A:C)','SIEMENS SIMATIC S7-300 CPU devices','CVE-2015-2177','Siemens SIMATIC是一款采用单一工程技术环境的自动化软件。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-300未能正确处理用户通过Proibus提交的发送给Port 102/TCP (ISO-TSAP)的报文，允许攻击者利用漏洞使应用程序崩溃。\r\n','https://ics-cert.us-cert.gov/advisories/ICSA-15-064-04  https://web.nvd.nist.gov/view/vuln/detail?vulnId=CVE-2015-2177','用户可参考如下厂商提供的安全补丁以修复该漏洞： \r\nhttp://subscriber.communications.siemens.com/',' Johannes Klick, Christian Pfahl, Martin Gebert, and Lucas Jacob ','Siemens SIMATIC拒绝服务漏洞（CNVD-2015-01606）的补丁','','2015-03-12 00:00:00','2015-03-13 00:00:00','2015-03-13 00:00:00','72973 ','2016-10-27 18:57:54','2016-10-27 18:57:54','Siemens SIMATIC拒绝服务漏洞','',NULL),(9,'CNVD-2015-00585','2015-01-26 00:00:00','中 (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:N/I:P/A:N)','SIEMENS SIMATIC S7-1200 <4.1','CVE-2015-1048 ','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200是模块化PLC控制器。 \r\n\r\nintegrated web server on Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU devices with firmware 4.1之前的版本存在打开重定向漏洞，允许远程攻击者将用户重定向通过未指定向量重定向用户任意的 web站点并进行网络钓鱼攻击。\r\n','http://www.siemens.com/innovation/pool/de/forschungsfelder/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-597212.pdf  http://secunia.com/advisories/62233  http://web.nvd.nist.gov/view/vuln/detail?vulnId=CVE-2015-1048','目前没有详细的解决方案，请到厂商的主页下载： \r\nhttp://www.siemens.com/ ',' SIEMENS','','','2015-01-22 00:00:00','2015-01-26 00:00:00','2015-01-26 00:00:00','72282','2016-10-27 18:56:05','2016-10-27 18:56:06','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200打开重定向漏洞','',NULL),(10,'CNVD-2014-05089','2014-08-19 00:00:00','高 (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:N/I:N/A:C)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500 1.6','CVE-2014-5074','Siemens SIMATIC是一款采用单一工程技术环境的自动化软件。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1500存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可利用此漏洞发起拒绝服务攻击。\r\n','http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/69241','用户可以联系供应商获得补丁信息： \r\nhttp://www.siemens.com',' Arnaud Ebalard from Agence Nationale de la SÃ©curitÃ© des SystÃ¨mes dâ??Information (ANSSI)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500拒绝服务漏洞（CNVD-2014-05089）的补丁','','2014-08-18 00:00:00','2014-08-20 00:00:00','2014-08-20 00:00:00','69241','2016-10-27 18:55:30','2016-10-27 18:55:30','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500拒绝服务漏洞','',NULL),(11,'CNVD-2014-02657','2014-04-28 00:00:00','中 (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:N/I:P/A:P)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 2.x\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1200 3.x\r\n','CVE-2014-2909 ','Siemens SIMATIC是一款采用单一工程技术环境的自动化软件。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1200存在HTTP头注入漏洞。由于某些未明输入再被使用显示HTTP头之前未能正确过滤，攻击者可以利用漏洞任意的HTTP头在响应发送给用户。\r\n','http://secunia.com/advisories/58173/  http://osvdb.com/show/osvdb/106256','用户可参考如下供应商提供的安全公告获得补丁信息： \r\nhttp://www.siemens.com/innovation/pool/de/forschungsfelder/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-892012.pdf',' Ralf Spenneberg, Hendrik Schwartke, and Maik BrÃ¼ggemann from OpenSource Training','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 HTTP头注入漏洞的补丁','','2014-04-25 00:00:00','2014-04-28 00:00:00','2014-04-28 00:00:00','67061','2016-10-27 18:55:00','2016-10-27 18:55:01','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 HTTP头注入漏洞','SA58173 OSVDB:106256',NULL),(12,'CNVD-2014-01910','2014-03-24 00:00:00','中 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:N/I:N/A:P)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 3.x','CVE-2014-2250 ','SIMATIC S7-1200是可编程控制器，可实现简单却高度精确的自动化任务。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1200向TCP端口443发送特制的数据包造成错误，攻击者可利用漏洞使设备进入defect模式。 \r\n','http://secunia.com/advisories/57441/','厂商已提供升级补丁，请及时下载更新： \r\nhttp://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-654382.pdf',' Ralf Spenneberg, OpenSource Training','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200拒绝服务漏洞（CNVD-2014-01910）的补丁','','2014-03-21 00:00:00','2014-03-24 00:00:00','2016-03-15 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 18:54:07','2016-10-27 18:54:07','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200拒绝服务漏洞','SA57441',NULL),(13,'CNVD-2014-01911','2014-03-24 00:00:00','中 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:P/I:N/A:N)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 3.x','CVE-2014-2252 ','SIMATIC S7-1200是可编程控制器，可实现简单却高度精确的自动化任务。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1200存在信息泄露漏洞，由于随机生成器内弱熵相关错误，可导致劫持另外用户的会话。 \r\n','http://secunia.com/advisories/57441/','厂商已提供升级补丁，请及时下载更新： \r\nhttp://www.siemens.com/cert/pool/cert/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-654382.pdf\r\n',' Alexander Timorin and Alexey Osipov, Positive Technologies','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200信息泄露漏洞的补丁','','2014-03-21 00:00:00','2014-03-24 00:00:00','2016-03-15 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 18:53:33','2016-10-27 18:53:34','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200信息泄露漏洞','SA57441',NULL),(14,'CNVD-2014-01720','2014-03-17 00:00:00','高 (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:P/I:P/A:C)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500 1.x','CVE-2014-2251 ','Siemens SIMATIC是一款采用单一工程技术环境的自动化软件。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1500使用的随机数生成器使用低熵，S7-1500 PLC所使用的WEB服务器验证使用该随机数进行验证存在安全漏洞，允许攻击者利用漏洞劫持WEB会话。\r\n','http://www.siemens.com/innovation/pool/de/forschungsfelder/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-456423.pdf','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500 1.5.0已经修复该漏洞，建议用户下载更新： \r\nhttp://www.automation.siemens.com/mcms/programmable-logic-controller/en/simatic-s7-controller/s7-40',' Dmitry Serebryannikov, Ilya Karpov, Alexey Osipov, Yury Goltsev, Alex Timorin, Alexey Osipov, and Ilya Karpov from Positive Technologies','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500不充分熵漏洞的补丁','','2014-03-14 00:00:00','2014-03-17 00:00:00','2014-03-17 00:00:00','66195','2016-10-27 18:52:35','2016-10-27 18:52:36','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500不充分熵漏洞','',NULL),(15,'CNVD-2014-01722','2014-03-17 00:00:00','中 (AV:N/AC:M/Au:N/C:N/I:P/A:N)','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500 1.x','CVE-2014-2248','Siemens SIMATIC是一款采用单一工程技术环境的自动化软件。 \r\n\r\nSiemens SIMATIC S7-1500集成的WEB服务器未能正确处理用户提交的输入，允许远程攻击者利用漏洞重定向用','http://www.siemens.com/innovation/pool/de/forschungsfelder/siemens_security_advisory_ssa-456423.pdf','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500 1.5.0已经修复该漏洞，建议用户下载更新： \r\nhttp://www.automation.siemens.com/mcms/programmable-logic-controller/en/simatic-s7-controller/s7-400/cpu/Pages/Default.aspx',' Dmitry Serebryannikov, Ilya Karpov, Alexey Osipov, Yury Goltsev, Alex Timorin, Alexey Osipov, and Ilya Karpov from Positive Technologies','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500重定向漏洞的补丁','','2014-03-14 00:00:00','2014-03-17 00:00:00','2014-03-17 00:00:00','','2016-10-27 18:52:00','2016-10-27 18:52:00','Siemens SIMATIC S7-1500重定向漏洞','',NULL),(16,'CNVD-2015-08446','2015-12-24 00:00:00','高 (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)','Schneider Electric Modicon M340','CVE-2015-7937','Schneider Electric Modicon M340 PLC BMXNOx和BMXPx都是法国施耐德电气（Schneider Electric）公司的可编程控制器产品。GoAhead Web Server是其中的一款嵌入式Web服务器。 \r\n\r\nSchneider Electric Modicon M340 PLC BMXNOx和BMXPx设备的GoAhead Web Server中存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可借助HTTP Basic Authentication数据中较长的密码利用该漏洞执行任意代码。\r\n','https://ics-cert.us-cert.gov